{"type": "article", "id": 35834, "title": "Nike营收超预期，以及，Vetements创始人被选为年度时尚人物 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-12-21T02:45:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 2145, "name": "Converse"}, {"id": 7350, "name": "瑞士手表"}, {"id": 10635, "name": "Visvim"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 19308, "name": "日本品牌"}, {"id": 36022, "name": "开口笑"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161221103652ijWLXOgqn5BN9uFr.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/nike-tops-estimates-delivering-win-in-its-second-quarter-10731898/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Nike 财年第二季度销售和净收入均超预期 </b></a>| Nike 公布财年的第二季度数据，在截止至 11 月 30 日三个月内，净收入增长了 7%，至 8.42 亿美元。总销售额则达到了 81.8 亿美元。由于超出华尔街预期，Nike 的股价上涨了 1.7%，至 52.69 美元每股。不过，Nike 在这个季度中，北美的销售下降了 4%，该公司称其国内市场的下跌是“短暂的”异常现象。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/swiss-watch-exports-decline-in-november-2/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>11 月，瑞士手表出口额下降了 5.6% </b></a>| 瑞士手表的出口额下降至 18.6 亿瑞士法郎，这是今年 3 月以来最糟糕的结果之一。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/visvim-buffalo-check-20l-backpack\" rel=\"nofollow\">visvim 推出了格纹双肩背包</a>。这款背包采用了羊毛混纺结合麂皮材质，细节上加入了电脑隔层和侧边口袋。售价为 1428 美元，现已发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612210951326JeB4MRIqxdmUcVi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">马来西亚球鞋店<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/crossover-reebok-club-c\" rel=\"nofollow\">  CROSSOVER 与 Reebok 合作</a>，推出全白色 Club C 鞋款。这双鞋的鞋舌背面写有 Be Reasonable, Demand the Impossible 字样，鞋垫则印有球网图案。预计将于 12 月 23 日率先于 <a href=\"http://www.crossoverconceptstore.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">CROSSOVER </a>网店发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221095143MC4VmfBlAv86gX5J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221095144EKjrs6gpNLzQ75tH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665957\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221095151UAZj7bceLxTJrvts.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221095151fmHX6r79eIWuoBjR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665957\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>格鲁吉亚时装设计师 Demna Gvasalia 被选为<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/20/demna-gvasalia-person-of-the-year-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Business of Fashion 的 2016 年度人物</a>。Gvasalia 就是 Vetements 的品牌创始人，在去年被任命为 Balenciaga 品牌的设计总监。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221095215RadFD4huUies69LN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>日本街头品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/neon-signs-2017-spring-summer-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\"> NEON SIGN 发布 2017 春夏系列造型特辑</a>。该特辑由时尚摄影师 Mizutani Taro 掌镜，展现了品牌豹纹、亮色、火焰等大胆元素的运用。如果你喜欢今年大热的 umbalanced style 的话，NEON SIGN 也是个不错的选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221100523LP4JW3Bdm9yIFtxj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221100523j7zvFKUsVuJ8XM1n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221100523Vk4ptcKXHbl0xSWq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221100523YbpPwvMr2UDZhF3R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612211005237Kvda6UErfezoAOc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221100523UtLuCdZo9rM6AhGz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612211005236xMGcs80eIJ9FPkA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221100524tNMgZIvzClE5UdHT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221100524zgrQyqEAlK347pao.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/converse-jack-purcell-modern-leather\" rel=\"nofollow\">Converse 的全新皮革制开口笑系列即将登场</a>。该系列有黑白极简双色，它的鞋身均由高级山羊皮制作，鞋底部分则由 Phylon 鞋底和全掌足弓支撑技术组成。它将于12 月 23 日至 1 月 2 日期间，在 Converse 官网和指定门店限量发售，每双售价为 1099 元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221100543zUwMPitXqsfn6YCv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221100543Ng4GmwOzXU2xtr8k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221100544qEuwAZIypGzDhLXQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221100544PG129AgoVpaiN0Je.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221100544QTGagLt8ej6JIX9b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161221100558RuUVzOs4G2kfNdXI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/20/demna-gvasalia-person-of-the-year-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">highsnobiety</a></p>"}